{
  "comment_text": {
    "dhp92:6": "Rig Veda 1.25.7 says that Varuṇa “knows the track of birds flying through the midspace”. ",
    "dhp94:1": "Similar imagery is found at Kaṭha Upaniṣad 3.3–9. "
  },
